Summer is here, but we are still working! We found that ocassionally, the application gave an error when opening it, eventhough it was solved when rebooting the device. In this new version we have solved it and from now on you will be able to sign the operations without problems.

We're back from holidays and raring to go!
We have recently been working to improve the integration of CaixaBank Sign with the other apps. Now, CaixaBank Sign will open automatically when you sign transactions via the CaixaBank App.
We also have an improved way of explaining things to make everything easier for you.

Christmas is nigh and with it we're bringing you a new version of the app. These past few months we've been working on improving the design and we've also taken the opportunity to iron out some of the glitches you've told us about.
If you like the new way of signing into CaixaBank, why not give us a 5-star rating? That way you'll encourage more people to get CaixaBank Sign.

We're back with good news!

From now on, when you want to install the CaixaBank Sign app, you can do so 100% online from anywhere, without needing to go to your nearest branch or cash machine to pick up an activation code.

We hope you like the changes and we encourage you to give us a 5-star rating.
The year is underway and we're still raring to go! This update will make the application even more secure. You might not realise it but your user experience will be even better.

We are starting 2019 with our batteries fully charged. In this latest update we are fixing minor issues you reported to us, as well as, adding some user transparent technical enhancements that make the app work better

- New navigation bar that organizes and simplifies the usage of the application, giving preference to the operations and user management.
- Fix for the case that the user starts an operation in a device different to the usual one. User we’ll be guided to realize the operation successfully.

¡Volvemos con buenas noticias!

En esta nueva versión hemos añadido:
- Nueva barra de navegación, que organiza y simplifica el uso de la aplicación, dando preferencia a las operaciones y gestión de usuarios.
- Se resuelve la casuística de que el usuario inicie la operación desde un dispositivo diferente al suyo habitual. Se le guiará para realizar la operación con éxito.
